# Frontend Components

This guide provides an overview of the frontend components in the LocalCA application.

## Component Architecture

LocalCA uses a component-based architecture with Next.js and React:

- Pages are built from reusable components
- Components follow a consistent design system
- ShadcnUI provides base UI components
- Tailwind CSS for styling

## Core Components

### Certificate Management

- [components/certificate-details.tsx](mdc:components/certificate-details.tsx) - Displays detailed certificate information
  - Certificate properties
  - Validity information
  - Download options
  - Action buttons

- [components/certificate-table.tsx](mdc:components/certificate-table.tsx) - Table view of certificates
  - Sortable columns
  - Filtering options
  - Status indicators
  - Action buttons

- [components/create-certificate-form.tsx](mdc:components/create-certificate-form.tsx) - Form for creating certificates
  - Common name input
  - SAN input
  - Certificate type selection
  - Validity period selection

### Dashboard Components

- [components/dashboard-header.tsx](mdc:components/dashboard-header.tsx) - Main dashboard header
  - Navigation links
  - User information
  - Action buttons

- [components/ca-info-card.tsx](mdc:components/ca-info-card.tsx) - CA information display
  - CA certificate details
  - Validity period
  - Download options

- [components/system-status.tsx](mdc:components/system-status.tsx) - System status information
  - Certificate counts
  - Expiring certificates
  - System health

### Settings Components

- [components/settings-tabs.tsx](mdc:components/settings-tabs.tsx) - Settings page tabs
  - General settings
  - Email settings
  - ACME settings
  - API settings

## UI Component Library

The project uses ShadcnUI, a component library based on Tailwind CSS:

- [components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/button.tsx) - Button component
- [components/ui/card.tsx](mdc:components/ui/card.tsx) - Card component
- [components/ui/dialog.tsx](mdc:components/ui/dialog.tsx) - Dialog component
- [components/ui/form.tsx](mdc:components/ui/form.tsx) - Form components
- [components/ui/table.tsx](mdc:components/ui/table.tsx) - Table component
- [components/ui/tabs.tsx](mdc:components/ui/tabs.tsx) - Tabs component

## Data Fetching

- [data/ca/](mdc:data/ca) - CA data fetching
- [data/service/](mdc:data/service) - Service API clients
- [data/acme/](mdc:data/acme) - ACME client operations

